# Olympus Agent Pipeline

This project uses a team of 12 AI agents (the Olympus team) to manage a complete production pipeline from discovery to testing, with a reusable **Project Initializer** to bootstrap each new project.

## Starting a New Project
1. Follow `cursor/agents/init_project.md` — the reusable initializer
2. Place client briefing in `cursor/agents/zeus/input/briefing.md`
3. The pipeline starts automatically: Initializer → Zeus → Hermes → ...

## Agent Team
| Agent | God | Role | Folder |
|-------|-----|------|--------|
| Initializer | — | Project Setup | cursor/agents/init_project/ |
| Zeus | King of Gods | Master Orchestrator | cursor/agents/zeus/ |
| Hermes | Messenger God | Discovery | cursor/agents/discovery/ |
| Athena | Goddess of Wisdom | Product Strategy | cursor/agents/product_strategist/ |
| Apollo | God of Arts | Desktop UI/UX | cursor/agents/ui_ux_desktop/ |
| Artemis | Goddess of Hunt | Mobile UI/UX | cursor/agents/ui_ux_mobile/ |
| Hephaestus | God of Craft | Visual Refinement | cursor/agents/ui_ux_refiner/ |
| Poseidon | God of Seas | Frontend Dev | cursor/agents/frontend/ |
| Hera | Queen of Gods | Responsive Design | cursor/agents/responsive_specialist/ |
| Hestia | Goddess of Hearth | Animations | cursor/agents/polishing/ |
| Ares | God of War | Frontend QA | cursor/agents/frontend_qa/ |
| Hermes II | Semi-god | Mobile Testing | cursor/agents/mobile_tester/ |
| Perseus | Semi-god | Desktop Testing | cursor/agents/desktop_tester/ |

## Pipeline Flow
**Phase 0:** Init (setup, Git, clean) → **Phase 1:** Discovery → Strategy → UI/UX (Desktop + Mobile parallel) → Refinement → Frontend → Responsive → Animations → QA → Testing (Mobile + Desktop parallel) → **Phase 2:** Zeus Final Review → **Phase 3:** Deploy

## Communication
- Each agent reads from their `input/` folder and writes to their `output/` folder
- Zeus coordinates the pipeline and manages hand-offs between agents
- All agents use model: opus-4.6
- To start a new project, follow `cursor/agents/init_project.md`
